5.0 of 5 bubbles
Clean and Managed
Dec 2020
Even though the seas were too rough to swim - red flags out and authorities monitoring - My Khe beach is still glorious. For the moment, there's a lot of debris as Danang had recently suffered a number of storm hits. But, I still walked on the beach, jogged on the beach, and read my book on it. Plus, for history buffs, this is the famous "China Beach."
Written December 21, 2020
kingvikramaditya
Haridwar444 contributions
A clean beach within the city
Mar 2020 • Solo
My Khe Beach is one of those places where you could have fun with friends as well as spend some quality time with your near and dear ones. Stroll, walk, run, swim or just sit admiring the beauty of the gorgeous South China Sea, My Khe Beach fits all these descriptions. Just opposite to the other side of the street, is where you'll find the most awesome hotels and restaurants serving international cuisines. It'd not be an understatement to say that it's the most happening part of Danang!
Written March 16, 2020
