Beautiful Beach
Feb 2020
Lovely long beach, soft sand, always a breeze. Worth going just to watch the surfers. Sun loungers very cheap sun loungers (40,000 VND for the day). Nobody hassles you trying to sell trips, plenty of drinks for sale available along the beach. Warmest sea water I've ever been in.
