Very clean and beautiful beach, perfect for long walk with an amazing city view on the other side.
Feb 2024 • Business
Clean beach with very soft sand. Designated areas to swim in with a lifeguard watching. Beautiful surroundings and lights at night. Also in February the water was a great temperature - tepid - not really hot or cold. I've been to many beaches all over the world and this is one of the best beaches I've been too.
