Empty beach but has fishing nets
Nov 2022
Nice broad beach and gentle sea. Hardly any people because we were in front of what seemed to be a fishing area. Very few people swimming even way down where it was clear so you have it to yourself. A few plastic bags floating swirling around us takes off 1 star
